sources.title: Outsource | Full Action Movie | Bashar Atiyat | Noel Blanco | 2022
sources.description:
Outsource - A police chief hires an old friend, who is an international spy, to help him search for a wanted suspect in the Philippines. But when the chief dies and the evidence points to the spy, all hell breaks loose.
2022.  Stars: Bashar Atiyat, Noel Blanco, Thais Buchner

metadata.Plot: A Serious All-Business retired Assassin and Spy with his Silly and Over Dramatic Super Hacker Twin brother, along with a Fem-Fatal asset as a Gun Shadow, help their friend Chief of Police to take down a head of a Black-Market syndicate.
